com.graph

Class UndirectedGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.graph.Graph
      • com.graph.UndirectedGraph

  • public class UndirectedGraph
extends Graph
    Light-weight class to form UndirectedGraphs and operate on them. For a much flexible but heavy-weight class please check out jgrapht.
